title: ZINC - IDW Transformers In Chronological Order

IDW Transformers In Chronological Order [ZINC]
LOOKING FOR MORE COMICS JUST TYPE ZINC IN YOUR SEARCH BOX
Hi there,
If you are big fan of transformers like me and not sure where to start or maybe you want to see what all the fuss is about then this pack will hopefully be what you are looking for.
This Pack is complete run down of IDW Transformers chronological order of the comics per which the timeline of events is developing, this has taken a week or so to get all the comics together and list them in number order.  Yes i know the list below is not in number order but trust me when you open the folder they are.
If you wondering where Transformers Regeneration One is that follows the timeline that was original started in Marvel.  I may in a future update include that run as well let me know in the comments below if you want that as well.
If you going to host this pack somewhere i hope you will give credit where its due that's all i ask.
Until next time enjoy and remember
